         <component>
            <section ID="i4i_description_id_d9116fa2-3dd7-46f4-9166-09ba13f8ceeb">
               <id root="3174f3e1-648d-4663-a75a-b3ec33e4c769"/>
               <code codeSystem="2.16.840.1.113883.6.1" code="34089-3" displayName="DESCRIPTION SECTION"/>
               <title> DESCRIPTION </title>
               <text>
                  <paragraph>Povidone-Iodine is a broad-spectrum microbicide with the chemical formulas:</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>2-pyrrolidinone, 1- ethenyl-, homopolymer, compound with iodine; 1-vinyl-2-pyrrolidinone polymer, compound with iodine. The structural formula is as follows:</paragraph>
                  <renderMultiMedia referencedObject="id_48107f42-c137-4f9f-9e93-e6b102b93834"/>
                  <paragraph>BETADINE® 5% Sterile Ophthalmic Prep Solution contains 5% povidone-iodine (0.5% available iodine) as a sterile dark brown solution stabilized by glycerin. Inactive Ingredients: citric acid, glycerin, nonoxynol-9, sodium chloride, sodium hydroxide, and dibasic sodium phosphate.</paragraph>
               </text>
               <effectiveTime value="20110705"/>
               <component>
                  <observationMedia ID="id_48107f42-c137-4f9f-9e93-e6b102b93834">
                     <text> chemical </text>
                     <value xsi:type="ED" mediaType="image/jpeg">
                        <reference value="72287bb4-3f70-4e12-aaf3-cfff48e044f8-01.jpg"/>
                     </value>
                  </observationMedia>
               </component>
            </section>
