               <code codeSystem="2.16.840.1.113883.6.1" code="34069-5" displayName="HOW SUPPLIED SECTION"/>
               <title> HOW SUPPLIED </title>
               <text>
                  <paragraph>BETADINE® 5% Sterile Ophthalmic Prep Solution is packaged under sterile conditions and supplied in 1 fl.oz. (30 mL) form sealed blue HDPE bottles (NDC #42254-006-30).</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>Store at 15-25°C (59-77°F).</paragraph>
